Sumitomo Bank reveals problem loans . Sumitomo Bank Ltd has disclosed its restructured loans ( in billions of yen unless specified ) : end - Mar 97 end - Mar 96 Restructured loans 104 . 6 614 . 5 Bad loans 190 . 4 202 . 4 Non - performing loans 616 . 6 670 . 5 Loans to troubled clients 162 . 4 - - Total problem loans 1 . 07 trln 1 . 49 trlnRestructured loans are those on which interest rates have been cut to help corporate restructuring . Bad loans are to bankrupt firms and non - performing are those with interest payments in arrears by six months or more . Loans to troubled clients are mainly to the bank ' s non - bank affiliates . 
